morial service will be held at pm sunday august  0 at shepherd’s church street chapel with mr billy dale ecklund smith officiating military rites will be conducted by hubert m smith american legion post  hedrickrhodes vfw post  chapter  of the dav the family will receive friends pm saturday at the home of his sister barbara redmond print obituary back contact us  ·  get directions  ·  mobile version  ·  privacy  ·  terms of use     0   thos shepherd  son funeral directors    funeral home website by batesville inc       site manager login clarence h smith  hammond la  intelius sign in we found clarence h smith in hammond la clarence h smith intelius found that clarence h smith is a male between 0 and 0 years old from hammond la we have connected them to  addresses  phones and  relatives or associates get report now age clarence h smith is in his 0s clarence has lived in hammond la greensburg la amite la clarences relatives mary smith oneida smith ann smith karla webb clarence h smith zodiac signpisces gendermale get report now want to know more about clarence get a comprehensive background report find full phone numbers and other contact information when available all from billions of available public records continue below for more details about clarence or use our people search engine to find others get background check on clarence h smith get a criminal check on clarence h smith get a public record report on clarence h smith get a people search report on clarence h smith clarence h smiths contact information known cities lived in find out where clarence h smith has lived as well as clarence h smiths phone numbers and email addresses clarence h smith has lived in  states louisiana address for clarence h smith 0 w d hammond la has lived in hammond la greensburg la get full address report phone numbers associated with clarence h smith    greensburg la    greensburg la 0   greensburg la get full phone report email addresses associated with clarence h smith get email r